[08:35.80]	Ere break the smallest parcel of this vow.
[08:39.16]KING HENRY IV	A hundred thousand rebels die in this:
[08:42.23]	Thou shalt have charge and sovereign trust herein.
[08:46.14]	[Enter BLUNT]
